na Bryant]] (first name misspelled by a bank officer when she opened her company's first bank account)\n* [[Larrousse]] \u2013 [[G\u00e9rard Larrousse]]\n* [[Lauda Air]] \u2013 [[Niki Lauda]]\n* [[Lavazza]] \u2013 [[Luigi Lavazza]]\n* [[Laverda]] \u2013 Pietro Laverda\n* [[Lawrence Levy Productions]] \u2013 [[Lawrence Levy]]\n* [[Lazard]] \u2013 Alexandre Lazard, Simon Lazard, and Elie Lazard\n* [[LDS (automobile)|LDS]] \u2013 Louis Douglas Serrurier\n* [[Leatherman]] \u2013 [[Timothy S. Leatherman]]\n* [[Lee Enterprises]] \u2013 A. W. Lee\n* [[Leeann Chin]] \u2013 [[Leeann Chin (restaurateur)|Leeann Chin]]\n* [[Lehman Brothers]] \u2013 [[Henry Lehman]], Emanuel Lehman, and Meyer Lehman\n* [[J. Lehrenkrauss Corporation]]\n* [[Leica Camera]], [[Leica Geosystems]] and [[Leica Microsystems]] \u2013 Ernst Leitz II (Leitz Camera)\n* [[Esselte Leitz GmbH & Co KG|Leitz]] \u2013 [[Louis Leitz]]\n* [[LeMond Racing Cycles]] \u2013 [[Greg LeMond]]\n* [[Leslie speaker|Leslie]] \u2013 [[Donald Leslie]]\n* [[Lesney Products]] \u2013 [[Leslie Smith (businessman)|Leslie Smith]] and Rodney Smith\n* [[Levi Strauss & Co.]] \u2013 [[Levi Strauss]]\n* [[Li Ning (company)|Li Ning Company Limited]] \u2013 [[Li Ning]]\n* [[Liberty (department store)|Liberty]] \u2013 [[Arthur Lasenby Liberty]]\n* [[Lidl]] \u2013 named for Ludwig Lidl\n* [[Life (Formula One team)|Life]] \u2013 Ernesto Vita (surname is Italian for life)\n* [[Ligier]] \u2013 [[Guy Ligier]]\n* [[Lincoln National Corporation]] \u2013 to convey the integrity of U.S. President [[Abraham Lincoln]]\n* [[Linde Group]] \u2013 [[Carl von Linde]]\n* [[Lipton]] \u2013 [[Thomas Lipton]]\n* [[Lisa Frank Incorporated]] \u2013 [[Lisa Frank]]\n* [[Livingston International]] \u2013 [[Gerry Livingston]]\n* [[Liz Claiborne]] \u2013 [[Liz Claiborne (fashion designer)|Liz Claiborne]]\n* [[Lloyds Bank]] \u2013 [[Sampson Lloyd]]\n* [[Lloyd's of London]] \u2013 [[Lloyd's Coffee House|Edward Lloyd]]\n* [[Lockheed Corporation]] (to [[Lockheed Martin]])