ramac Racing|Pramac d'Antin]] \u2013 [[Luis d'Antin]]\n* [[Pressman Toy Corporation]] \u2013 Jack Pressman\n* [[PricewaterhouseCoopers]] \u2013 [[Samuel Lowell Price]], [[Edwin Waterhouse]], [[William Cooper (accountant)|William Cooper]]\n* [[Primanti Brothers]] \u2013 Joe Primanti, Dick Primanti, Stanley Primanti\n* [[Procter & Gamble]] \u2013 [[William Procter (candlemaker)|William Procter]] and [[James Gamble (industrialist)|James Gamble]]\n* [[Lutte Internationale|Promotions Varoussac]], original name of the wrestling promotion later known as Lutte Internationale \u2013 Frank Valois, Andr\u00e9 Roussimoff (aka [[Andr\u00e9 the Giant]]), Louis Accocella (aka [[Gino Brito]])\n* [[Prost Grand Prix]] \u2013 [[Alain Prost]]\n* [[PRS Guitars]] \u2013 [[Paul Reed Smith]]\n* [[Pye Ltd.|Pye]] \u2013 [[William George Pye]]\n\n==Q==\n* [[Quaife]] \u2013 Rod Quaife\n* [[Qvale]] \u2013 Bruce Qvale\n\n==R==\n* [[R. J. Reynolds Tobacco Company]] (RJR) \u2013 [[R. J. Reynolds]]\n* [[Railton (car)|Railton]] \u2013 [[Reid Railton]]\n* [[Rainer-Wurz.com]] \u2013 Markus Rainer and [[Alexander Wurz]]\n* [[Ralt]] \u2013 [[Ron Tauranac|Ron]] and Austin Lewis Tauranac\n* [[RAM Racing]] \u2013 Mike Ralph and John Macdonald\n* [[Rawlings (company)|Rawlings]] \u2013 George and Alfred Rawlings\n* [[RE Amemiya]] \u2013 Asami Amemiya\n* [[Rebaque]] \u2013 [[H\u00e9ctor Rebaque]]\n* [[Reiter Engineering]] \u2013 Hans Reiter\n* [[Renault]] \u2013 [[Louis Renault (industrialist)|Louis Renault]]\n* [[Team Rensi Motorsports|Rensi-Hamilton Racing]] \u2013 Ed and Sam Rensi, and [[Bobby Hamilton, Jr.]]\n* [[REO Motor Car Company]] \u2013 [[Ransom E. Olds]]\n* [[Reuters]] \u2013 [[Paul Reuter]]\n* [[Reynard Motorsport]] \u2013 [[Adrian Reynard]]\n* [[Richard Childress Racing]] \u2013 [[Richard Childress]]\n* [[Richard Petty Motorsports]] \u2013 [[Richard Petty]]\n* [[Rickenbacker]] \u2013 [[Adolph Rickenbacker|Adolph Rickenbacher]]\n* [[Riddell Sports Group, Inc.|Riddell]] \u2013 John Tate Riddell\n*