y:Fictional Jeet Kune Do practitioners]]\n[[Category:Fictional Shaolin kung fu practitioners]]\n[[Category:Fictional Ninjutsu practitioners]]\n[[Category:Fictional karateka]]\n[[Category:Fictional Brazilian jiu-jitsu practitioners]]\n[[Category:Fictional aikidoka]]\n[[Category:Fictional judoka]]\n[[Category:Fictional bojutsuka]]\n[[Category:Fictional Muay Thai practitioners]]\n[[Category:Fictional stick-fighters]]\n[[Category:Fictional victims of kidnapping]]\n[[Category:Fictional adoptees]]\n[[Category:Fictional detectives]]\n[[Category:Fictional business executives]]\n[[Category:Fictional hackers]]\n[[Category:Fictional orphans]]\n[[Category:Fictional vigilantes]]\n[[Category:Fictional gymnasts]]\n[[Category:Fictional military strategists]]\n[[Category:Superheroes who are adopted]]\n[[Category:Teenage characters in comics]]\n[[Category:Teenage characters in television]]\n[[Category:Robin (DC Comics)]]\n", "name_user": "Rodw", "label": "safe", "comment": "Disambiguating links toDuke Thomas(link changed toDuke Thomas (comics)) usingDisamAssist.", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tim_Drake"}
